1. Make sure you have latest version of android studio
2. Make sure you have following tools or SDK installed:
    a. Android SDK Build Tool
    b. Android SDK Platform-Tools
    c. Android SDK Tools
    d. Android Support Repository
    e. Android 5.0 SDK platform

    you can use SDK manager to install those
3. Use Android Studio to open exist project. select code
3. Once it finished gradle building, you can press the Run button in your Android studio
